Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:01:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The First Patient! The Untold\NStory Of The Rumble Ball"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it... Lashes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Wake up! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your passionate morning kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Don't give me\Nthat disgusting face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I wanna say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--It's an island! We can see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? An island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this island have monsters?\NI prefer big and strong ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't step on it. Don't step on it.\NDon't step on my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to\Nbe anything suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it looks like this is a small island, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect for making\Nnonperishable food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this island has tons of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Seems like it'd be a good idea to\Ncollect them and load them on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there're other plants\Nthat can be used for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island seems quite\Nenjoyable for a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Then please go look for things\Nthat can be used for food, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining four of you will do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--What is it?\N--Drawing lots?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three who draw the shortest lots\Nwill spend all day collecting these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who draws the longest one\Nwill stay here and watch the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you the one giving us orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Normally the captain\Nwould give orders, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey... they're all short.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why'd you draw three of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the one who grabs\Nthe most the winner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this ship has a\Ncaptain who can give orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously you aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew the longest one.\NSo I'll be watching the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Please look after the ship, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Hurry up! Let's go already!\NLet's go get fruits already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming too, right, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll spend all day today\Nmeasuring this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to put it on the sea chart.\NI can't wait to put my skills in practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later! Be careful! Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look after the ship, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who collects the most will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... what a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to take\Norders from that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here I go! Measuring! Measuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... How lively Nami-san is when she's\Ncarrying measuring tools on her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! You're lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mellorine! Mellorine!\N--Stop talking stupid and come already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all by myself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When no one's around, the ship\Nlooks really big somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys! I'll be the great\NCaptain Chopper from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone! Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Don't eat others' food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Prepare special dishes for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray, Captain Chopper! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been there?!\NBeing so quiet... How sneaky...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look! I still don't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a Baroque Works Officer Agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a rogue, and mean, and stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept you! Even if\NLuffy accepts you as a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way... I'd talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her special skill is assassination,\Nright? I hear she's very smart, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I went to bed after I\Nmade ten Rumble Balls last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spend all day making another ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble Balls... I have to\Nmake them when I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you never know when\Nyou'll run into enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this brings back memories of the\Ntime the Rumble Ball was created...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine won't notice if these get\Nreduced little by little, will she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always mixes this and this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Was it this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't put this one, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Do you know where\Nmy medicine bottles are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have important medicine in them.\NThey're all rare and valuable medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't be playing\Nwith them, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a good scolding\Nfrom Doctorine then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Doctorine is doing now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll write her a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--They're called... Rumble Balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to uncover\Nthe secret of the Rumble Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then assassinate me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance. I won't be taken\Ndown by someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ow!\N--Heavy Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horn Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see the power of the Rumble Ball?!\NThere's more where that came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see through your weak point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Point...! Scope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weak point...! Weak point...!\NWhere's her weak point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to look so fierce, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... Stop it! Stop it! Stop tickling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it!\N--How cute you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C... Cute...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break! Even if you like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't make me happy or anything!\NThere's no way I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! You jerk! You jerk...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, then... shall we go?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The water's gone, right?\N--Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to drink coffee... before I read.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You go draw\Nthe water... since you spilt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... How could I feel like\Nworking on such a fine day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! There sure are a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, I thought... "This is it...\NThis is the end of Captain Usopp...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was attacked by a huge condor...\Nand I couldn't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Because of that, I couldn't\Nget even a single fruit. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Don't worry about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh...! I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to take orders from\Nthat woman?! Seriously, how irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Dragon... Twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contour line should be like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The right ridgeline is 42 degrees, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love fever is also 42 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please measure the height of\Nmy feeling towards you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're in my way! Move!\N--Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's going to draw\Nthe water... Why is she coming, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fine day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really. It's a fine day. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... wanted to take a walk somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this way for quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was constrained every day for a\Nlong time, so... I never smiled, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, you said you've\Nalways been alone since you were eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... By following pirates,\NI barely survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me... about this Doctorine person...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking about that person earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a doctor, right? Is she your teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, but Doctorine is someone\Nwhom I'm deeply indebted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call her Dr. Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.47,0:15:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kureha... What kind of person is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really loves alcohol. Although\Nshe's a woman, she's like a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's like a pirate, but she is a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I studied to be a doctor\Nunder Doctorine for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:16:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"After mixing these three kinds\Nof herbs, grind them well"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read the medical book?\NThe 500 pages that I told you to read?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! You were playing\Nwith the medicine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I've been studying for three years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've also read 200 medical books.\NLet me compound the medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.50,0:16:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still 100 years too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've memorized all 200\Nbooks that I read! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even memorized "The Seventh\NPrinciple" by Dr. Alexandra,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which you said was the most difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The TaboTabo bacteria start\Ndividing on the 7th day of culturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After showing the sign of overreaction
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:17:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mentioned on page 1,254,\Nchapter 7, section 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph... So... wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I got a febrile disease\Nfrom the patient I saw the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a terrible fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, if you talk big like that,\Ntry putting your medical skill to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your first patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give you any advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail, I'll die...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn by experience that\Nmedicine is a serious challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where patients' lives are at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the blue-nose reindeer be\Nable to win in a serious challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake! This is\Nthe pathogen of the Mondolin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What works for this\Npathogen is... let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna ask what\Nmedicine I compounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think there're patients out there\Nwho'd have enough composure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to ask doctors questions about everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If patients don't trust their doctors,\Nthey won't recover from the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Do you feel a little better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy. No medicine\Nwould work that quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me sleep a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad, considering\Nyour lack of experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time that\NDoctorine praised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the only time during those six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of acknowledging me,\Nshe left her life in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Doctorine.\NThat's the kind of person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget... Some day, I'll become\Na doctor that'll surprise even her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I said too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better get going or the sun will set...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had someone that I could\Nwrite a letter to... like you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... why weren't you able\Nto get even a single fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge king condor attacked me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everyone... I tried\Nrisking my life to get fruits,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't... I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, Zoro did a great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up that momentum and stay\Nup all night tonight to get more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... How lovely Nami-san is, even\Nwhen she efficiently gives orders...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! You lecher cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight?! Moss Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, today was the first\Npeaceful day in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? What did you\Ndo all day today on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a pretty good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I run towards\Nto see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the helm and opened the\Nmiraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for the sky and sought out\Nmy dreams, though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream; when I met you,\NI discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.56,0:22:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a bit of courage,\NI gained something grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for my "wish"\Nto become my "pledge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the tale of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my feelings\Nin a brand new wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.05,0:22:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase after you\Nwherever you go, Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sanji-kun... Please! There's\Nsomething I want you to buy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything for you... Uhm...\Nthese papers cost 4.8 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wouldn't have that\Nmuch money, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't be so cold.\N--That's right. We do have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. In exchange for this\Nguy with a bounty on his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uprising of the Navigator!\NFor the Unyielding Dream!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.56,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
