Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:01:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.08,0:01:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is this rain going to stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp, have you got anything fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I've got a firework we\Ncould launch, but just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wanna do that?\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it. What if there's a\Nhostile ship nearby, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that book you've been\Nreading this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is showing interest in a book?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The book is called "Rainbow Mist,"\Nor "Niji no Kiri."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a novel, based on some\Nadventures this person had
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in an unusual region of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventures, huh? That sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how bored he might be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea sure is a strange place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.23,0:03:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I saw an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Will Make it Bloom!\NUsopp the Man and the Eight-Foot Shell"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's okay, right, Mommy and Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, keep close watch on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.94,0:03:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's a town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A town!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a small town, but it sure is lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to procure\Na few things here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, are you going to do some shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, get a load of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.25,0:04:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me there are wanted\Nposters! No, that's not it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a firework festival!\NAnd what's more, it's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--Fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen fireworks in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Nami-san, I shall be your escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh, no thanks. Mind your own self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, huh? I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you folks around before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to watch the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that isn't why--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, are these fireworks that well-known?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a famous festival on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been holding it\Nfor 400 years, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,400 years? That long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. You see that tower up\Non the mountain behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who live in that house\Nhave been making fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for generations, since 400 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an old man and a little girl\Nthat live there right now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then, does the old man\Nmake the fireworks by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! He makes them\Ntogether with the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They bang them out all\Nyear long, just for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it take a whole\Nyear to make fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dense! You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's all sorts of reasons. If I\Ntold you, you wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, okay.\N--That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like we were\Nalmost out of gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'd share a little with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who knows?\N--I'll be back in a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I hope that nothing like\Nwhat went on last year happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what went on last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Last year, at the fireworks festival--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadoyan! They came here\Nto have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to go out of your\Nway to tell them about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's nothing. Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! We should tell\NZoro and Robin about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's go tell Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, maybe we should eat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how a firework\Nof my making turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show this to them,\Nand they'll be so impressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and say, "if you're skilled enough\Nto make something this wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then please, take as much\Ngunpowder as you like, for free!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what a face you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really the head firework maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betcha! I'm Boss Odama,\Nthe pyrotechnist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'm begging you.\NYou can spare a little, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have lots of gunpowder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any gunpowder\Nto give to a greenhorn like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, be on your way, please. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a minute! Please, decide if I'm\Na novice or not after looking at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fairly decent--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:25.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"14th generation Odama"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So round! So huge! So white!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to\Ncome across my threshold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old-timer, is that real?!\NThat's papier-mâché, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would papier-mâché be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lying around a fireworks master's home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for real. So, "this is a\Nfairly decent" what, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A three-gauge shell, huh?\NIt's pasted together a little loose,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's still pretty well put together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you hiding it?\NIt would be a waste not to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kodama, the granddaughter\Nof Grandpa Odama over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're the girl that makes fireworks\Ntogether with the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't have you looking down\Non me, just because I'm little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still pretty skillful, maybe even\Nas much as Grandpa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ee-yow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go getting carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to\Ncontact the launch team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did! They're going to be here\Nshortly to carry the shells away,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I would\Nget them out, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, you've got\Nto prepare the mortars,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get the wagon ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there, go give her a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?\N--Just get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about? He tells me\Nto go away, then tells me to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up. I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fixing to slack off? Help me out, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not here to become an apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. I just came to\Nget some gunpowder from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had your own firework,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought for sure you\Nwanted to be an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made that one for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but I'm\Nnot up to working pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but it's true,\Nthat is well put-together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should hurry up and finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to mention it, you said\Nthe same thing before, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I thought\Nit was already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks only become finished\Nwhen they blossom beautifully
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the night sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why all of the fireworks in\Nthe storehouse are unfinished goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These launching mortars, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not finished until\Nthey're used as equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something amazing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I told you. I won't have\Nyou looking down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, that ridiculously huge\Nfirework earlier is the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still unfinished, right? I sure\Nwould like to see that one go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, we tried to\Nlaunch one just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There was another one like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't work.\NOur equipment was flawed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mommy and my daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They died, a year ago today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the launch of the\N200-gauge shell went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This weather seems kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still hold the firework\Nfestival if it's raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's no use, Mommy, Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least get things ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's no use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it clears up tonight, I'm planning\Non launching the 200-gauge shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Fireworks aren't food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't raise your voice, you dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't launch something\Nas huge as that on your own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. I asked the launch\Nteam to help me out in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it already failed to launch\Nonce, right? It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get the launch\Nteam folks caught in it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not. They'll just be\Nsetting it up, and then take cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the launching by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"By yourself," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! I'm telling your grandpa,\Nand putting a stop to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was going to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go ruining my\NMommy and Daddy's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Mommy and Daddy's dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our family has been making\Nfireworks for generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for over 400 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, that's okay...\N--Just let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, we once had the technical skill
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make and launch 200-gauge shells,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at some point,\Nthat tradition was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my Mommy and Daddy's\Ndream to bring back that skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, tonight,\NI'm going to finish their dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second. Why would you\Njust blab something like that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to keep\Nyour grandpa occupied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The launch team folks will be\Nhere soon to carry the shell away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While they're doing that,\Nkeep Grandpa occupied inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he doesn't come out here. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb fool! How can I help you\Nout with something so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:59.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"14th generation Odama"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because my Mommy and Daddy's\Ndream is still only half-finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to finish it for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A prayer before launching?\NA fine thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't what you'll be launching.\NYou'll be doing smaller ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The launch team... Why did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say. They were\Nthinking of you when they told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! After all the begging I did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kodama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just too reckless.\NThat thing is sure to misfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that for sure,\Ndo you?! I'm not afraid of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:15:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though they don't know\Nhow those of us left behind feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what it means\Nto carry on their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kodama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, well, we'll get things ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if you would, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you're getting ready,\Neven with the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This rain will let up soon.\NThe wind is coming in from the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kodama is the only one\Nwho doesn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, has that structure\Nbeen there the whole 400 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit upon a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about hearing me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are graves? Wow, they're funky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy and Daddy, like I said,\Nif this long spell of rain ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it means that I have your permission,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I can launch the 200-gauge shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, does this mean I'm wrong, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It doesn't mean you're wrong. Kodama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you launch your own fireworks,\Nwe'd be glad to stop the rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, Mommy and Daddy, your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you think that's all our dream is?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You are our dream. Our dream\Nis that you will carry on for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become a fine pyrotechnist."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kodama, take your time, and\Nmake your own 200-gauge shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an unlimited\Namount of time, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kodama, if you can bring\Nback the 200-gauge shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will also make our dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let Grandpa take care\Nof our 200-gauge shell;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you keep on showing us your\Nbeautiful fireworks up in heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, someday, I'll make my\Nown 200-gauge shell, you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks for understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, as promised..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a messenger, sent from heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp... Angel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thank you! I'll try my best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is coming off nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I have to admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using the wheel on the\Ncart in the yard as a pulley,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he figured out the trick for dragging\Nthat thing out of the storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought that the\Ntower that's been here for 400 years
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was actually the launch\Nplatform for 200-gauge shells...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is this kid, anyhow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"14th generation Odama"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes the rapid fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Last one!\N--Okay, last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that shabby firework just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how my first firework turned out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Old Man Odama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy and Daddy's firework...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to make a firework like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy and Daddy really were amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll be able to make\Na firework like that someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy! Daddy! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, can I have some gunpowder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:22:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.95,0:23:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to catch a cold dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who catch colds are people\Nwho let their mind's guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wonder if someone\Nsomewhere is spreading stories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.58,0:23:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about Zoro, the pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once called myself a pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fabled Pirate Hunter!\NZoro, the Wandering Swordsman"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
